{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3a12191d68","title":"中共中央给各区各地方委员会各独立组组长的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"181b012fda","index":0,"year":1924,"month":8,"day":31,"articleId":"3a12191d68"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji3","name":"毛泽东全集第3卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji3.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b2bc7a18f4","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央给各区各地方委员会","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"3a12191d68"},{"id":"aa665c5e9e","type":"paragraph","text":"各独立组组长的通知”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"3a12191d68"},{"id":"cbce805cdd","type":"paragraph","text":"（1924年8月31日）为准备召开第四次全国大会，要求各地同志对于本党一年来的各种政策、各种实际工作，提出意见，报告中央局。个人有特别意见的，可以写成书面意见，由委员会或组长汇寄中央局。中央拟将各地讨论的意见，在党报上发表，以为第四次大会各项决议讨论的材料。[1]这是毛泽东签发的关于召开第西次全国代表大会准各意见致各区名地方委员会各独立组组长的通知的主要内容。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"3a12191d68"}],"page":{"id":"21ed1628ad","publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"3a12191d68","start":97,"end":97}}}},"__N_SSG":true}